title: BigFish Games - Flux Family Secrets The Ripple Effect with Strat
description:
Flux Family Secrets: The Ripple Effect - 141.18 MB


New Treasure Chest: Felix's Favorites Game!
A mysterious family has contacted you and holds the secrets of your past! Fix the errors in time 

in this exciting Hidden Object game and take your rightful place in the Flux family! Explore 

famous historical sites like Hatshepsut`s tomb, the Wright Brothers` workshop, Benjamin 

Franklin`s study and many more. Flux Family Secrets: The Ripple Effect has you realign the 

timeline by finding misplaced objects scattered through time and solving clever puzzles.



    * Explore historical sites
    * Solve tricky puzzles
    * Fix the flux!



System Requirements:
OS: Windows XP/Vista
CPU: 1.0 GHz
RAM: 512 MB
DirectX: 7.0
Hard Drive: 150 MB
